{"tid":593506,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反白眼記者遭封殺　名字變禁詞","createTime":"2018-03-15T05:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T06:25:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6b0422e2020108b86aa24e5d3e5c99b3707a34","tid":593506,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180315/20332316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332316&d=CfYj5Sot4Mn2GrTY8971y6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=ca842b4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332316&h=9ee35848\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180315/20332316</a><br />\n<br />\n反白眼記者遭封殺　名字變禁詞<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/a1603a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2Fa1603a.gif&h=bf666526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁相宜因反白眼（圓圖）意外成網絡紅人。<br />\n<br />\n兩會女記者史詩級反白眼哄動全球，卻受到內地互聯網全面封殺，女記者梁相宜反白眼圖片一張不留，「梁相宜」列為微博禁詞。美國《紐約時報》指出，梁女反白眼一幕戳穿全國人大會議的虛偽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美媒：戳穿人大虛偽<br />\n<br />\n受第一財經女記者梁相宜史詩級白眼啟發，內地網民改圖瘋傳；淘寶出售印有梁相宜頭像的T恤和手機套；梁的微博粉絲人數迅速攀升到20多萬。有網民指梁「代表大多數人，翻了我們不敢翻的白眼」。微信上，人們還把梁的藍衣和被她「藐爆」的女記者張慧君的紅衣賦予政治解讀，指張穿的是紅色，即中國和中共的顏色，許多人卻表明自己支持藍黨。<br />\n<br />\n被梁反白眼的張女，來自據報是中共喉舌《人民日報》海外網美國頻道「全美電視台」。有網友認為，這兩位記者都是在「搶戲」，都是為了出風頭。<br />\n<br />\n政治評論員鄧聿文在Twitter上評論：「今天兩位紅藍女士火了，我想說的是，你假裝一本正經開兩會，我假裝一本正經提問，然後她一本正經地厭惡她，喜劇效果就出來了。極權統治下，一切表演無不具有喜劇效果，是笑話，除了極權本身。」<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》/英國廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/a1603b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2Fa1603b.gif&h=31e962c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反白眼一幕被設計成潮Tee。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t倡騰籠換鳥　累珠三角港廠房倒閉<br />\n兩岸要聞 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t廈門企業遭中證監罰68億破紀錄<br />\n兩岸要聞 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t汪洋全票當選政協主席港澳三前特首連任副主席　董建華得票最少<br />\n兩岸要聞 7小時前"},{"pid":"cbaa857618e1a2649d3db8e604d86bfca9d47f02","tid":593506,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"整容失敗樣"},{"pid":"50b10b8c3301ebe10fb1739b42b12a63edaf224c","tid":593506,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"正tee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863d27bb6da417b4729a99d60436ab8e0cd1fa18","tid":593506,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/a1603b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2Fa1603b.gif&h=31e962c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}